title: Hit the Road!
description: Time to leave Vilnius behind! Flexible departure depending on when everyone's ready for the scenic hour drive.

title: Arrival at Lake Paradise
description: Welcome to Moletai! Simple, warm welcome to our lakeside adventure base after the pleasant drive.

title: Campfire Chronicles & Chill Vibes
description: Kick back around the fire! Optional games, music, and that perfect Friday night relaxed energy. No pressure, just good vibes.

title: Slovenian Breakfast Bonanza
description: Rise and shine, Slovenia! Keep it easy, keep it social, keep it delicious.

title: Lithuanian Landing Party
description: The Lithuanians have arrived! Time for welcome drinks and the real party to begin.

title: Meet & Greet Madness
description: Name tags, icebreakers, and the beautiful chaos of new friendships being born!

title: Mixed-Culture Quiz Battle
description: Slovenians vs Lithuanians? Nah! Mixed teams for maximum cultural chaos and fun!

title: Freedom Hour
description: Music, hammocks, optional activities - basically do whatever makes your soul happy!

title: Lunch & Munch
description: Proper sit-down meal to fuel up for the afternoon adventures ahead.

title: Park Explorer Mission
description: Guided tour of the park - perfect for digesting lunch with some light movement and nature vibes.

title: Splash Zone & Sports Spectacular
description: Water games, sports, drinks, and chats - the perfect combo for Saturday afternoon energy!

title: Snack Attack & Evening Prep
description: Free time with snacks - the perfect transition from day vibes to evening magic.

title: Evening Program Extravaganza
description: Dance floor is OPEN! Time to show off those moves and party like it's 2025!

title: Slow Motion Morning
description: Wake up slowly with coffee, quiet music, and peaceful morning walks. No rush, just vibes.

title: Brunch & Heart-to-Hearts
description: The perfect time to eat, chat, and soak in those last precious moments together.

title: Pack-Up & Memory Lane
description: Last hugs, final photos, and maybe some guestbook signing for the memories!

title: Road Trip Back to Vilnius
description: Time for our Slovenian friends to hit the road back to Vilnius. Safe travels on the scenic drive!
